        "duration": 3.999
    },
    {
        "text": "cornered hat men wore at the time",
        "start": 15.04,
        "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
        "text": "then the bowler was invented around 1850",
        "start": 17.279,
        "duration": 6.801
    },
    {
        "text": "as a lower alternative to the top hat",
        "start": 20.0,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
