        "start": 33.44,
        "duration": 5.68
    },
    {
        "text": "known to use them to produce rabbits",
        "start": 35.92,
        "duration": 5.52
    },
    {
        "text": "at the hat factory workers spray a fine",
        "start": 39.12,
