        "start": 84.08,
        "duration": 5.359
    },
    {
        "text": "however the felt is still malleable so",
        "start": 86.88,
        "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
        "text": "to reactivate the stiffener and lock in",
        "start": 89.439,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "the shape they set the head aside for",
